 inc since  she serves as a member of canadian advisory board at catalyst inc she served as a director at walmart de mexico sab de cv since march  she served as a nonexecutive director of massmart holdings limited from july   to november   she served as a trustee of st leo university she served as a member of board of advisors of h lee moffitt cancer center  research institute she served as a director of united way of tampa bay ms broader obtained a bachelor of arts degree from washington state universityread full background corporate headquarters  metro parkwayfort myers florida united statesphone fax  board members memberships presentnon executive independent directorraymond james financial incpresentceo president  directorchicos fas inc education ba washington state universitypullman other affiliations raymond james financial inchannaford bros co incmichaels stores incwalmart stores incsweetbay supermarket incetablissements delhaize frères et cie le lion groupe delhaize sawalmart de méxico sab de cvwashington state universitypullmanwalmart canada corpmassmart holdings limitedcatalyst inc annual compensation salarybonustotal annual compensation stocks options restricted stock awardsall other compensation total compensation total annual cash compensationtotal short term compensationother long term compensationtotal calculated compensation request profile update   the information and data displayed in this profile are created and managed by sp global market intelligence a division of sp global bloombergcom does not create or control the content for inquiries please contact sp global market intelligence directly by clicking here stock quotes market data is delayed at least  minutes company lookup competitor compensationnamepositioncompanycompensationfabian t garcia chief executive officer president and directorrevlon incmmorris goldfarb chairman of the board and chief executive officergiii apparel group ltdmroger l rawlins chief executive officer and inside directord